================================================================================
HITAEXT CHANGES
================================================================================

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Final version released at end of DAESO project.

- hitaext source now depends on the Daeso Framework library
- fixed relative path bug, so relative document file paths are now by default 
  interpreted relative to the dir containing the alignment file 
- id-based alignment in addition to n-based alignment,
  depending on the value of the "method" attribute
  (either "n" or "id") on the "alignment" element
- alignment files have default extension "ptc" (for "parallel text corpus")
- alignment file (parallel text corpus) can be passed as command line argument

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.5.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- first public release of Hitaext